Olive Christelle Ngo Nyepel ( onye amụrụ n'abalị̀ iri na isii nke ọnwa Jenụwarị n'afọ 1995), nke a maara dị ka Christelle Nyepel, bụ onye na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba dịka onye na-agba egwuregwu ọ̀nọ̀ n'etiti
A mụrụ ya ma zụlite ya na Cameroon, ọ bụ nwa amaala Equatorial Guinea ma na-egwuri egwu maka otu ụmụ nwanyị nke mba ahụ
Ọ bụ otu n'ime ndị otu Equatorial Guinea na 2011 FIFA Women's World Cup, na-mpụta ugboro atọ
Na klọb ọ gbara bọọlụ nye Estrellas de E'Waiso Ipola na Equatorial Guinea.
